Package: tiledbsoma
Type: Package
Title: TileDB SOMA
Description: Interface for working with 'TileDB'-based Stack of Matrices,
    Annotated ('SOMA'): an open data model for representing annotated matrices,
    like those commonly used for single cell data analysis.
Version: 0.0.0.9022
